  <bioghist id="aspace_6d9cb5a4a24c7c03f52d55b5c8ceb696">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Psychologist.</p><p> Cornell University Class of 1947, Columbia University Ph.D. 1955.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_9dd734f77357a77135383df41640544e">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Papers of Dr. Joyce Brothers include correspondence, subject files, letters received, scripts, clippings, contracts, awards, photographs, cartoons, slides, and articles and books by Dr. Brothers. Audiovisual Archives of Dr. Joyce Brothers include 463 motion picture films, ca. 796 video tapes, and 184 audio recordings.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite id="aspace_13bf6b06a2679550629774473bacf249">
    <head>Cite As:</head>
<p>Dr. Joyce Brothers papers, #4254. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
